What MetaForge does (plain English)

We turn messy, scattered data into clean, labeled, compliant datasets that AI companies can actually use.

Not just raw data—metadata + context + structure.

⸻

Core product

1) Metadata Enrichment Engine

* Takes raw data (text, images, logs, etc.)
* Adds:
    * labels
    * relationships
    * context tags
    * quality scores
* Outputs training-ready datasets

⸻

2) Curated Data Packs

Pre-built datasets for:

* LLM fine-tuning
* recommendation systems
* sentiment / behavior models
* domain-specific AI (legal, medical, retail, etc.)

⸻

3) Data Pipelines (B2B)

* Companies plug in their internal data
* MetaForge:
    * cleans it
    * structures it
    * annotates it
* Returns AI-ready data layer

