How you get data (important)

Do NOT rely on shady scraping.

Use:

* public, licensed datasets
* opt-in user contributions (pay or incentivize)
* partnerships with platforms
* synthetic + human-labeled augmentation

This keeps you:

* legal
* scalable
* sellable to big companies

